IT'S A PLACE RESERVED
FOR THE DUELING ELITE.

00:01:21.615 --> 00:01:25.553
HMM. I GUESS THAT MEANS
WE'LL FIT RIGHT IN.

00:01:25.553 --> 00:01:26.620
UH...

00:01:26.620 --> 00:01:28.122
WOULD YOU MIND
TELLIN' HOUSEKEEPIN'

00:01:28.122 --> 00:01:30.024
THAT I LIKE MY PILLOWS
EXTRA FLUFFY?

00:01:30.024 --> 00:01:30.991
URRRHHH!

00:01:30.991 --> 00:01:32.226
YOU'RE A DOLL.

00:01:33.227 --> 00:01:36.630
LAST ONE, AND...

00:01:36.630 --> 00:01:37.698
VOILà.

00:01:38.866 --> 00:01:41.769
AT LAST! WE'RE FINALLY
AT THE CASTLE!

00:01:42.937 --> 00:01:44.038
URRHH...

00:01:44.038 --> 00:01:45.239
HUH?

00:01:45.239 --> 00:01:46.607
NO, NO, NO!

00:01:46.607 --> 00:01:49.377
YOU THREE DON'T EVEN
HAVE DUELING GLOVES.

00:01:49.377 --> 00:01:51.212
ARRHH!
BUT YOU HAVE TO
LET US IN.

00:01:51.212 --> 00:01:52.346
WE'RE THE CHEERLEADERS.

00:01:52.346 --> 00:01:53.981
CHEER WHAT?!

00:01:53.981 --> 00:01:55.883
WHAT DO YOU LOSERS
THINK THIS IS,

00:01:55.883 --> 00:01:57.618
A HIGH SCHOOL
FOOTBALL GAME?!

00:01:57.618 --> 00:02:00.521
NO STAR CHIPS, NO ENTRY!
YOU GOT THAT?

00:02:00.521 --> 00:02:01.822
Mai: YOU'RE SAYING
YOU COULDN'T DO US

00:02:01.822 --> 00:02:03.491
THIS ONE LITTLE FAVOR?

00:02:03.491 --> 00:02:04.492
HUH?

00:02:04.492 --> 00:02:06.026
NO EVEN FOR ME?

00:02:06.026 --> 00:02:07.561
HMM?
UH...

00:02:07.561 --> 00:02:11.565
UH...ABSOLUTELY NOT.
PEGASUS GAVE ME
EXPLICIT INSTRUCTIONS

00:02:11.565 --> 00:02:14.068
NOT TO LET ANYONE--
WHAT? HEY!

00:02:14.068 --> 00:02:15.069
OHHH!

00:02:16.404 --> 00:02:18.305
STOP! OHH!

00:02:19.774 --> 00:02:22.209
HMM. AND
THAT'S THAT.

00:02:22.209 --> 00:02:24.879
YOU LITTLE
THUMBSUCKERS!
OPEN THIS DOOR!

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:26.847
THERE'S NO TIME
TO WASTE.

00:02:27.915 --> 00:02:30.217
Joey:
YOU HEARD THE MAN.
LET'S GO!

00:02:30.217 --> 00:02:31.919
[THINKING] THE SOONER
I FIND PEGASUS,

00:02:31.919 --> 00:02:33.621
THE SOONER I CAN FIND
MY GRANDPA.

00:02:40.694 --> 00:02:41.929
HEY! ISN'T THAT--

00:02:41.929 --> 00:02:43.697
Joey:
BANDIT KEITH.

00:02:43.697 --> 00:02:45.132
I CAN'T STAND
THIS GUY.

00:02:45.132 --> 00:02:46.133
HUH?

00:02:46.133 --> 00:02:47.468
WELL, WHAT
DO YA KNOW?

00:02:47.468 --> 00:02:49.203
IF IT ISN'T
BIG, TOUGH JOEY

00:02:49.203 --> 00:02:51.071
AND HIS WHOLE CREW
OF DUELIN' DUMMIES.

00:02:51.071 --> 00:02:53.507
YOU SLIME BUCKET!
I'VE BEEN WAITIN'
TO FIND YOU

00:02:53.507 --> 00:02:55.342
EVER SINCE YOU
LEFT US TRAPPED
IN THAT CAVE.

00:02:55.342 --> 00:02:56.610
GRRR!

00:02:56.610 --> 00:02:58.245
YAAHH!

00:02:58.245 --> 00:02:59.246
MISSED ME.

00:02:59.246 --> 00:03:01.182
WHOOPS. TOO SLOW.

00:03:01.182 --> 00:03:02.917
CAN'T THIS LITTLE GRUDGE
OF YOURS WAIT?

00:03:02.917 --> 00:03:03.918
YOU WISH, CREEP.

00:03:03.918 --> 00:03:05.986
OK. SUIT YOURSELF.

00:03:05.986 --> 00:03:08.589
BUT THE REAL ACTION
IS ABOUT TO START.

00:03:08.589 --> 00:03:09.590
THE <i>REAL</i> ACTION?

00:03:09.590 --> 00:03:10.858
HUH?
HUH?

00:03:10.858 --> 00:03:14.028
Keith:
YEAH, THE WORLD CHAMP
AND PEGASUS.

00:03:14.028 --> 00:03:15.029
WHOA!

00:03:17.465 --> 00:03:18.599
IT'S KAIBA!

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:20.167
I'D HOPED
TO GET FIRST CRACK

00:03:20.167 --> 00:03:21.836
AT THE OLD MAN
MYSELF, BUT YOU KNOW

00:03:21.836 --> 00:03:23.637
THEY SAVE
THE BIGGEST MATCH
FOR LAST.

00:03:23.637 --> 00:03:26.173
WAIT A MINUTE.
ARE YOU SAYING THOSE TWO
ARE GONNA DUEL?

00:03:26.173 --> 00:03:27.808
THAT IS CORRECT.
HUH?

00:03:27.808 --> 00:03:29.810
WELCOME, FINALISTS.
I'M CROQUET,

00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:31.712
CHIEF TOURNAMENT LIAISON.

00:03:31.712 --> 00:03:33.447
CONGRATULATIONS
ON MAKING IT

00:03:33.447 --> 00:03:35.616
THIS FAR.
PEGASUS
IS QUITE TAKEN

00:03:35.616 --> 00:03:37.318
WITH ALL OF YOUR
DUELING TALENTS.

00:03:37.318 --> 00:03:39.420
IN FACT, HE'S
SO IMPRESSED,
HE WANTED

00:03:39.420 --> 00:03:41.455
TO REWARD YOU
WITH SOME ENTERTAINMENT--

00:03:41.455 --> 00:03:43.324
A SPECIAL
EXHIBITION MATCH.

00:03:43.324 --> 00:03:45.693
I THINK YOU'LL ALL
BE QUITE IN AWE

00:03:45.693 --> 00:03:47.828
OF WHAT YOU'RE
ABOUT TO SEE. HMM.

00:03:47.828 --> 00:03:49.830
THIS MATCH SHOULD
GIVE YOU AN IDEA

00:03:49.830 --> 00:03:51.765
OF WHAT'S IN STORE
FOR ALL OF YOU.

00:03:51.765 --> 00:03:54.502
SO BASICALLY, IT'S MEANT
TO INTIMIDATE US, HUH?

00:03:54.502 --> 00:03:57.438
WHY WOULD PEGASUS
DO SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

00:03:57.438 --> 00:03:59.540
'CAUSE HE'S
A GRADE-A NUT CASE.

00:03:59.540 --> 00:04:02.142
[CHUCKLES]
ENJOY THE MATCH.

00:04:03.477 --> 00:04:05.446
OH...
MAN.

00:04:05.446 --> 00:04:07.882
Yugi, thinking: THIS
SHOULD BE INTERESTING.

00:04:07.882 --> 00:04:10.751
[THINKING] LITTLE BROTHER,
I'M HERE FOR YOU NOW,

00:04:10.751 --> 00:04:13.854
AND I WON'T LET
ANYTHING STOP ME
FROM RESCUING YOU.

00:04:13.854 --> 00:04:14.855
[RUMBLING]

00:04:14.855 --> 00:04:15.856
HUH?

00:04:20.060 --> 00:04:21.896
[SOFT CHUCKLE]

00:04:25.625 --> 00:04:26.626
[CHUCKLES]

00:04:26.626 --> 00:04:27.994
WHERE'S MY BROTHER?

00:04:30.062 --> 00:04:31.797
WHAT? NO "HELLO"?
NO "HOW ARE YOU?"

00:04:31.797 --> 00:04:34.333
I THOUGHT WE WERE FRIENDS,
KAIBA BOY.

00:04:34.333 --> 00:04:36.435
DON'T TELL ME
THAT MY KIDNAPPING MOKUBA

00:04:36.435 --> 00:04:38.037
AND SEIZING CONTROL
OF YOUR COMPANY

00:04:38.037 --> 00:04:40.139
HAS PUT A RIFT
BETWEEN US.

00:04:40.139 --> 00:04:42.108
IT WAS NOTHING PERSONAL.

00:04:42.108 --> 00:04:44.143
BESIDES, IT'S NOT LIKE
I HURT YOUR KID BROTHER.

00:04:44.143 --> 00:04:45.411
HE'S PERFECTLY SAFE.

00:04:45.411 --> 00:04:48.014
IN FACT, YOU CAN
HAVE HIM BACK IF YOU LIKE.

00:04:48.014 --> 00:04:50.283
JUST BEAT ME IN A DUEL
LIKE WE AGREED,

00:04:50.283 --> 00:04:51.584
AND I'LL HAND HIM OVER.

00:04:51.584 --> 00:04:54.120
I MEAN, ONE LITTLE VICTORY
SHOULDN'T BE A PROBLEM

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.122
FOR THE DUEL MONSTERS
WORLD CHAMP.

00:04:56.122 --> 00:04:57.990
[THINKING]
THAT MILLENNIUM EYE
PEGASUS HAS

00:04:57.990 --> 00:05:01.761
COULD MAKE IT
A REAL BIG PROBLEM,
EVEN FOR KAIBA.

00:05:01.761 --> 00:05:03.396
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M SAYING THIS,

00:05:03.396 --> 00:05:06.265
BUT I'M <i>NOT</i> HOPIN'
KAIBA LOSES THIS DUEL.

00:05:06.265 --> 00:05:08.501
I STILL SAY HE'S
A FIRST-CLASS JERK

00:05:08.501 --> 00:05:09.869
FOR EVERYTHING
HE PUT US THROUGH,

00:05:09.869 --> 00:05:11.337
BUT I CAN'T HELP
BUT FEEL FOR HIM,

00:05:11.337 --> 00:05:13.005
TRYIN' TO GET HIS
KID BROTHER BACK.

00:05:13.005 --> 00:05:15.875
FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,
ANYONE WHO STANDS UP
TO PEGASUS

00:05:15.875 --> 00:05:17.643
CAN'T BE ALL BAD.
MM-MMM.

00:05:17.643 --> 00:05:19.679
[THINKING] JOEY
AND TRISTAN ARE RIGHT.

00:05:19.679 --> 00:05:21.914
AFTER ALL, WHAT
COULD BE MORE NOBLE

00:05:21.914 --> 00:05:24.350
THAN FIGHTING FOR SOMEONE
THAT YOU LOVE?

00:05:24.350 --> 00:05:26.419
I JUST HOPE THAT KAIBA
HAS LEARNED TO FIGHT

00:05:26.419 --> 00:05:29.422
WITH HIS HEART
AS WELL AS HIS HEAD.

00:05:29.422 --> 00:05:31.591
COME NOW, KAIBA,
IT'S SO GAUCHE

00:05:31.591 --> 00:05:32.959
TO KEEP US
IN SUSPENSE,

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:35.361
ESPECIALLY
WITH AN AUDIENCE
WAITING IN THE WINGS.

00:05:35.361 --> 00:05:37.129
HUH?

00:05:37.129 --> 00:05:38.598
HEY THERE, KAIBA.

00:05:38.598 --> 00:05:42.768
YUGI! HOW COULD
YOU BE IN HERE
AFTER I DEFEATED YOU?

00:05:42.768 --> 00:05:45.238
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN
YOU'D FIND A WAY.

00:05:45.238 --> 00:05:46.906
[THINKING]
<i>I</i> CERTAINLY DID.

00:05:46.906 --> 00:05:48.774
YUGI HAS PASSED
ALL THE TESTS

00:05:48.774 --> 00:05:50.509
THAT I HAVE
PRESENTED HIM WITH.

00:05:52.011 --> 00:05:53.512
I HOPE YOU'RE READY,
KAIBA.

00:05:53.512 --> 00:05:56.048
I'VE BEEN LOOKING
FORWARD TO THIS
FOR QUITE SOME TIME.

00:05:56.048 --> 00:05:57.683
Kaiba: GOOD.

00:05:59.552 --> 00:06:00.987
OHHH!

00:06:00.987 --> 00:06:03.356
Kaiba: THEN YOU'LL
HAVE NO PROBLEM
DUELING WITH THIS.

00:06:03.356 --> 00:06:04.423
HUH?

00:06:05.925 --> 00:06:07.126
WELL?

00:06:07.126 --> 00:06:08.594
YOU WANT TO DUEL ME

00:06:08.594 --> 00:06:10.062
WITH YOUR LATEST
CONTRAPTION?

00:06:10.062 --> 00:06:13.132
BUT I DON'T EVEN KNOW
HOW THE SILLY DEVICE
EVEN WORKS.

00:06:13.132 --> 00:06:14.800
DO I SPIN IT
LIKE A TOP...

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:16.736
OR ROLL IT
LIKE A BALL?

00:06:16.736 --> 00:06:18.271
CUT THE THEATRICS!

00:06:18.271 --> 00:06:19.905
OOOHH!

00:06:19.905 --> 00:06:21.807
KAIBA MEANS BUSINESS.

00:06:21.807 --> 00:06:24.010
OK, THEN. HOW ABOUT
WE SETTLE THIS

00:06:24.010 --> 00:06:25.511
LIKE BUSINESSMEN WOULD?

00:06:25.511 --> 00:06:27.513
I'LL AGREE
TO USE YOUR SYSTEM

00:06:27.513 --> 00:06:29.715
IF YOU AGREE TO A REQUEST
THAT <i>I</i> HAVE.

00:06:29.715 --> 00:06:30.950
WHAT?

00:06:30.950 --> 00:06:33.486
NOTHING THAT WILL CHANGE
THE GAME, OF COURSE.

00:06:33.486 --> 00:06:37.590
I JUST WANT SOMEONE ELSE
TO OPERATE YOUR LITTLE
DEVICE FOR ME.

00:06:37.590 --> 00:06:39.025
I SMELL A RAT.

00:06:39.025 --> 00:06:40.293
[CHUCKLES MALEVOLENTLY]

00:06:40.293 --> 00:06:41.527
I ASSURE YOU,

00:06:41.527 --> 00:06:43.863
I'LL STILL MAKE ALL
THE STRATEGIC DECISIONS.

00:06:43.863 --> 00:06:45.998
THE GAME PLAY
WON'T CHANGE AT ALL.

00:06:45.998 --> 00:06:47.233
SO WHY THE REQUEST?

00:06:47.233 --> 00:06:48.567
WHY NOT FIGHT
YOUR OWN BATTLE

00:06:48.567 --> 00:06:49.669
FOR ONCE IN YOUR LIFE?

00:06:49.669 --> 00:06:50.836
[CHUCKLES]

00:06:50.836 --> 00:06:52.672
[THINKING]
SIMPLE-MINDED FOOL.

00:06:52.672 --> 00:06:55.207
FOR ALL YOUR TITLES
AND TECHNICAL INNOVATIONS,

00:06:55.207 --> 00:06:58.177
YOU STILL HAVEN'T
LEARNED THAT FIGHTING
ISN'T THE ONLY WAY

00:06:58.177 --> 00:07:00.279
TO INFLICT DAMAGE
UPON AN OPPONENT.

00:07:00.279 --> 00:07:05.818
A MAN'S SPIRIT CAN BE BROKEN
IN MUCH EASIER WAYS.

00:07:07.787 --> 00:07:10.156
SHOW KAIBA THE LAD
WHO'LL PLAY AS MY PAWN,

00:07:10.156 --> 00:07:11.724
AND HE'LL UNDERSTAND
MY REQUEST.

00:07:13.726 --> 00:07:14.727
[GASPS]

00:07:17.163 --> 00:07:18.297
KAIBA'S BROTHER!

00:07:21.767 --> 00:07:22.902
MOKUBA!

00:07:25.104 --> 00:07:26.072
IT'S ME.

00:07:26.072 --> 00:07:27.440
SOMETHING'S
NOT RIGHT.

00:07:27.440 --> 00:07:29.475
IT'S LIKE HE'S
BEEN HYPNOTIZED.

00:07:29.475 --> 00:07:32.912
Pegasus: I APOLOGIZE
IF HE DOESN'T SEEM
QUITE LIKE HIMSELF.

00:07:32.912 --> 00:07:35.181
BUT I HAPPEN TO FIND
THAT THE CAPTIVES I KEEP

00:07:35.181 --> 00:07:38.584
ARE FAR EASIER TO MANAGE
AFTER I'VE MADE
AN EXTRACTION OF SORTS.

00:07:38.584 --> 00:07:40.019
YOU MONSTER!

00:07:40.019 --> 00:07:41.387
[CHUCKLES EVILLY]

00:07:42.388 --> 00:07:43.956
NOW, NOW, KAIBA BOY.

00:07:43.956 --> 00:07:45.825
PETTY INSULTS
AREN'T THE WAY

00:07:45.825 --> 00:07:47.426
TO GET YOUR BROTHER'S
SOUL BACK.

00:07:47.426 --> 00:07:49.662
HA HA HA HA HA!
OHHH!

00:07:49.662 --> 00:07:51.097
Bakura:
HIS SOUL?!

00:07:51.097 --> 00:07:52.832
WHAT'S PEGASUS
MEAN?

00:07:52.832 --> 00:07:55.534
HE MUST'VE DONE
TO MOKUBA WHAT HE DID
TO YUGI'S GRANDPA.

00:07:55.534 --> 00:07:57.770
HEH HEH HEH
HEH HEH.

00:07:57.770 --> 00:07:59.905
I TOLD YOU
YOUR LITTLE BROTHER
WAS PERFECTLY SAFE,

00:07:59.905 --> 00:08:04.910
AND HE IS. BUT HOW LONG
HE REMAINS THAT WAY
IS UP TO YOU.

00:08:04.910 --> 00:08:08.114
BEAT ME IN A DUEL,
AND I'LL RELEASE HIM
AS PROMISED.

00:08:08.114 --> 00:08:11.784
BUT FAIL, AND
NOT ONLY WILL <i>HIS</i> SOUL
REMAIN IN BONDAGE,

00:08:11.784 --> 00:08:14.086
BUT YOURS WILL JOIN IT.

00:08:18.017 --> 00:08:19.252
TO SAVE YOUR BROTHER,
YOU'LL HAVE TO DEFEAT ME.

00:08:19.252 --> 00:08:21.087
DEFEAT YOU?
I'LL CRUSH YOU!

00:08:21.087 --> 00:08:23.589
[THINKING]
I HAD NO IDEA!

00:08:23.589 --> 00:08:25.424
I KNEW PEGASUS
KIDNAPPED MOKUBA,

00:08:25.424 --> 00:08:28.427
BUT I HAD NO CLUE
THAT HE SNATCHED
HIS SOUL, TOO.

00:08:28.427 --> 00:08:30.263
[GASPS] OF COURSE!

00:08:30.263 --> 00:08:33.266
THAT'S WHY KAIBA
WENT TO SUCH LENGTHS
TO BEAT ME.

00:08:33.266 --> 00:08:35.101
HIS BROTHER'S
EVEN WORSE OFF
THAN HE THOUGHT.

00:08:35.101 --> 00:08:37.169
MOKUBA'S LIKE
MY GRANDPA NOW.

00:08:37.169 --> 00:08:39.538
I HAVE TO HELP KAIBA
ANY WAY I CAN.

00:08:39.538 --> 00:08:42.241
Pegasus: SO IT'S SETTLED.
WE'LL USE YOUR NEW INVENTION,

00:08:42.241 --> 00:08:44.944
BUT YOUR BROTHER
WILL OPERATE IT FOR ME.

00:08:44.944 --> 00:08:46.345
WAIT! PEGASUS!

00:08:46.345 --> 00:08:49.682
WHAT'S THE MATTER,
KAIBA BOY?
THIS WAS YOUR IDEA.

00:08:49.682 --> 00:08:52.585
USING YOUR OWN SYSTEM
IS SURE TO GIVE YOU
QUITE THE ADVANTAGE.

00:08:52.585 --> 00:08:53.953
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

00:08:53.953 --> 00:08:56.589
[THINKING] OHHH!
I CAN'T DUEL
MY OWN BROTHER,

00:08:56.589 --> 00:08:59.292
EVEN IF HIS SOUL
<i>IS</i> IN ANOTHER PLACE.

00:08:59.292 --> 00:09:01.327
[LAUGHING] WHAT'S UP,
BIG BROTHER?

00:09:01.327 --> 00:09:04.363
[WEEPING]
I MISS YOU, KAIBA.

00:09:04.363 --> 00:09:06.699
YOU CAME FOR ME!

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.202
HE'S BEEN THROUGH
ENOUGH ALREADY.

00:09:10.202 --> 00:09:13.272
OK, THEN, PEGASUS.
YOU WIN.

00:09:13.272 --> 00:09:14.907
WE WON'T USE IT.

00:09:14.907 --> 00:09:16.208
BUT THAT'S
HIS EDGE!

00:09:16.208 --> 00:09:18.144
WE'LL DUEL
ON YOUR TERMS.

00:09:18.144 --> 00:09:20.646
JUST KEEP
MY LITTLE BROTHER
OUT OF THIS.

00:09:20.646 --> 00:09:22.515
SO RATHER THAN DUEL
YOUR EMPTY SHELL

00:09:22.515 --> 00:09:23.849
WITH THE DEVICE
HE'S PERFECTED,

00:09:23.849 --> 00:09:26.085
HE'LL GIVE ME
HOME FIELD ADVANTAGE.

00:09:26.085 --> 00:09:27.520
FINE WITH ME.
TAKE HIM AWAY.

00:09:30.723 --> 00:09:32.158
YOU CREEP.

00:09:32.158 --> 00:09:35.594
WATCH YOURSELF, KAIBA.
YOU'RE IN <i>MY</i> WORLD NOW.

00:09:35.594 --> 00:09:37.630
UHH! OHH...

00:09:38.731 --> 00:09:41.567
WOW! CHECK OUT
THE AUTOMATED BRIDGE!

00:09:41.567 --> 00:09:43.803
OHHH!
OH!

00:09:43.803 --> 00:09:45.271
Téa:
FORGET THE BRIDGE!

00:09:45.271 --> 00:09:47.473
AN ENTIRE ARENA'S
COMING DOWN!

00:09:47.473 --> 00:09:50.109
THAT, OR
THE BIGGEST ELEVATOR
EVER BUILT!

00:09:53.579 --> 00:09:55.481
THIS SHOULD BE GOOD.

00:09:55.481 --> 00:09:56.916
HMM.

00:09:56.916 --> 00:09:59.218
Mai: THE 2 BIGGEST LEGENDS
IN DUEL MONSTERS

00:09:59.218 --> 00:10:00.920
GOING AT IT?

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:03.622
THIS IS WHAT
IT'S ALL ABOUT.

