[OSCILLATING TONE]

00:10:33.853 --> 00:10:35.287
READY, KAIBA?

00:10:35.287 --> 00:10:37.790
YOUR BROTHER'S FATE
HANGS IN THE BALANCE.

00:10:37.790 --> 00:10:39.759
[CHUCKLES
MALEVOLENTLY]

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:42.495
KAIBA, YOU GOTTA
BELIEVE IN THE HEART
OF THE CARDS!

00:10:42.495 --> 00:10:44.430
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
TO RESCUE MOKUBA!

00:10:44.430 --> 00:10:48.134
HUH? KEEP OUT OF THIS.
I'M FIGHTING THIS DUEL
MY WAY.

00:10:48.134 --> 00:10:49.368
JUST DON'T FORGET
THAT IT TAKES

00:10:49.368 --> 00:10:50.603
MORE THAN
A STRONG MONSTER

00:10:50.603 --> 00:10:52.505
AND CLEVER STRATEGIES
TO WIN THIS.

00:10:52.505 --> 00:10:54.974
THAT MILLENNIUM EYE
PEGASUS HAS
CHANGES EVERYTHING.

00:10:54.974 --> 00:10:56.042
YOU HAVE TO--

00:10:56.042 --> 00:10:57.777
YUGE, DON'T FORGET
KAIBA'S THE GUY

00:10:57.777 --> 00:10:59.145
WHO TOOK
5 OF YOUR STARS.

00:10:59.145 --> 00:11:01.547
I KNOW. BUT I ALSO KNOW
WHAT IT'S LIKE

00:11:01.547 --> 00:11:03.549
TO BE DUELING FOR SOMEONE
YOU CARE ABOUT,

00:11:03.549 --> 00:11:05.317
AND I COULDN'T
LIVE WITH MYSELF

00:11:05.317 --> 00:11:08.254
IF I HELD BACK ON ANYTHING
THAT COULD HELP KAIBA
GET HIS BROTHER BACK!

00:11:08.254 --> 00:11:09.922
EASY, BUDDY.

00:11:09.922 --> 00:11:14.026
YUGI, YOU'RE A GOOD DUELIST,
BUT I DON'T NEED YOUR HELP.

00:11:14.026 --> 00:11:16.228
IT'S MY BATTLE
TO FIGHT NOW,

00:11:16.228 --> 00:11:18.364
AND I WILL WIN.

00:11:20.833 --> 00:11:22.334
[CHUCKLES] POOR FOOL.

00:11:22.334 --> 00:11:24.770
HE NEEDS ALL THE HELP
THAT HE CAN GET.

00:11:24.770 --> 00:11:27.840
WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER
FOR A LONG TIME,

00:11:27.840 --> 00:11:29.308
AND NOW WE'LL SEE
IF THE MASTER

00:11:29.308 --> 00:11:32.211
IS THE DUEL MONSTERS
CREATOR OR THE CHAMPION!

00:11:32.211 --> 00:11:35.681
YOU HAVE NOWHERE LEFT
TO HIDE, PEGASUS.

00:11:35.681 --> 00:11:36.916
TIME TO DUEL!
TIME TO DUEL!

00:11:45.925 --> 00:11:49.295
LOOK AT YOU--
THE FIRST MOVE, AND
ALREADY YOU'RE NERVOUS.

00:11:49.295 --> 00:11:51.230
HERE. DEFENSE MOVE.

00:11:51.230 --> 00:11:52.431
FEEL BETTER?

00:11:52.431 --> 00:11:54.333
OH, AND I'LL PLAY
THIS CARD, TOO.

00:11:54.333 --> 00:11:56.936
BUT I THINK I'LL KEEP IT
FACE DOWN FOR NOW,

00:11:56.936 --> 00:11:58.404
JUST TO KEEP YOU GUESSING.

00:11:58.404 --> 00:11:59.839
[THINKING] I DOUBT THAT.

00:11:59.839 --> 00:12:02.341
PEGASUS MUST ALREADY
BE SCHEMING SOMETHING.

00:12:02.341 --> 00:12:04.577
IT'S MY TURN NOW.

00:12:04.577 --> 00:12:05.778
[THINKING] HMM...

00:12:05.778 --> 00:12:07.513
BLUE EYES
ON MY FIRST DRAW.

00:12:07.513 --> 00:12:10.249
NOT BAD. BUT I CAN'T
RISK ATTACKING WITH HIM

00:12:10.249 --> 00:12:13.252
UNTIL I HAVE
A BETTER IDEA OF WHICH
CARD PEGASUS PUT DOWN.

00:12:13.252 --> 00:12:16.622
STILL, THAT DOESN'T
MEAN I CAN'T ATTACK
WITH SOMETHING ELSE.

00:12:19.525 --> 00:12:21.827
I'LL LAY A CARD
FACE DOWN, TOO.

00:12:23.729 --> 00:12:27.299
AND ALSO I PLAY
RUDE KAISER FACE UP,

00:12:27.299 --> 00:12:28.667
IN ATTACK MODE.

00:12:32.138 --> 00:12:33.672
Kaiba: GO, RUDE KAISER!

00:12:33.672 --> 00:12:35.441
ATTACK PEGASUS'
DEFENSE CARD

00:12:35.441 --> 00:12:37.643
WITH FOREARM SLASH!

00:12:40.946 --> 00:12:42.581
OH, NO!

00:12:42.581 --> 00:12:44.483
I'D EXPECT MORE
FROM YOU, PEGASUS.

00:12:44.483 --> 00:12:47.253
I HAD NO IDEA THAT YOU
HAD SUCH POWERFUL CARDS

00:12:47.253 --> 00:12:49.288
AT YOUR DISPOSAL, KAIBA.

00:12:49.288 --> 00:12:51.657
I DON'T THINK I HAVE
A BEAST IN MY ENTIRE DECK

00:12:51.657 --> 00:12:53.425
THAT COULD COMPARE
WITH <i>THAT</i> CREATURE.

00:12:56.095 --> 00:12:59.265
HOLD ON. I MAY HAVE
SPOKEN TOO SOON.

00:12:59.265 --> 00:13:01.233
YES, HERE'S
THE PERFECT CARD--

00:13:01.233 --> 00:13:02.434
PARROT DRAGON.

00:13:03.435 --> 00:13:04.837
[RAHRR]

00:13:04.837 --> 00:13:07.173
ATTACK!
BOMBARDING BEAK!

00:13:07.173 --> 00:13:09.108
NOT SO FAST.
I PLACED A CARD

00:13:09.108 --> 00:13:10.342
FACE DOWN, TOO,
REMEMBER?

00:13:10.342 --> 00:13:11.544
YOU WHAT?

00:13:11.544 --> 00:13:14.580
AND I'M ACTIVATING
ITS MAGIC RIGHT NOW.

00:13:14.580 --> 00:13:16.215
THE MESMERIC
CONTROL CARD

00:13:16.215 --> 00:13:19.051
ENTRANCES YOUR
MONSTER AND REDUCES
ITS ATTACK POWER

00:13:19.051 --> 00:13:20.819
BY 800 POINTS.

00:13:23.455 --> 00:13:25.658
[AWK AWK]

00:13:25.658 --> 00:13:27.393
[AWK AWK]

00:13:27.393 --> 00:13:29.762
KAISER, FOREARM SLASH!

00:13:29.762 --> 00:13:31.330
CARVE UP THAT BIRD!

00:13:31.330 --> 00:13:33.499
[AWK AWK AWK--]

00:13:34.867 --> 00:13:36.936
OH, NO!

00:13:36.936 --> 00:13:39.872
[THINKING] WAIT.
SOMETHING'S WRONG HERE.

00:13:39.872 --> 00:13:42.341
I DON'T GET IT.
PEGASUS TALKS
A BIG GAME

00:13:42.341 --> 00:13:43.676
BUT DUELS
LIKE A KID.

00:13:43.676 --> 00:13:45.344
IT'S ALMOST
LIKE HE'S TOYING
WITH HIM.

00:13:45.344 --> 00:13:47.112
YEAH. WAIT!

00:13:47.112 --> 00:13:49.048
DIDN'T HE PULL
THIS ACT WITH YOU?

00:13:49.048 --> 00:13:51.083
YEP. I GUESS

00:13:51.083 --> 00:13:53.919
HE DOESN'T EVEN TAKE
THE WORLD CHAMPION
SERIOUSLY.

00:13:53.919 --> 00:13:57.122
Yugi: I JUST HOPE
KAIBA CATCHES ON
BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE.

00:13:57.122 --> 00:14:00.893
HA HA HA HA HA HA!

00:14:04.887 --> 00:14:05.854
[THINKING]
SOMETHING'S NOT RIGHT.

00:14:05.854 --> 00:14:07.156
THIS IS ALL TOO EASY.

00:14:07.156 --> 00:14:09.258
PEGASUS DOESN'T EVEN
SEEM TO BE TRYING.

00:14:09.258 --> 00:14:10.993
I'VE TAKEN OUT
2 OF HIS MONSTERS

00:14:10.993 --> 00:14:12.761
WITHOUT HIM EVEN
PUTTING UP A FIGHT.

00:14:12.761 --> 00:14:15.197
IT'S ALMOST LIKE HE
EXPECTED ME TO DO IT...

00:14:15.197 --> 00:14:18.333
LIKE HE KNEW EXACTLY
HOW I WAS GOING
TO ATTACK HIM.

00:14:20.063 --> 00:14:22.332
MY TURN, PEGASUS.

00:14:22.332 --> 00:14:24.735
[THINKING] HMM.
ANOTHER GOOD CARD.

00:14:24.735 --> 00:14:26.270
BUT IF I'M RIGHT
ABOUT PEGASUS

00:14:26.270 --> 00:14:27.871
AND HE <i>IS</i>
JUST PLAYING WITH ME,

00:14:27.871 --> 00:14:29.540
HE MIGHT BE ABLE
TO COUNTER IT.

00:14:29.540 --> 00:14:30.941
[HUMMING]

00:14:30.941 --> 00:14:33.544
[THINKING] I'M NOT
FALLING FOR THIS BIT.

00:14:33.544 --> 00:14:35.679
NO WAY. I'LL JUST
PLAY SOMETHING

00:14:35.679 --> 00:14:37.447
THAT I KNOW HE CAN'T
DEFEND AGAINST--

00:14:37.447 --> 00:14:39.049
MY BLUE EYES!

00:14:39.049 --> 00:14:40.183
STOP RIGHT THERE!

00:14:40.183 --> 00:14:41.351
HUH?

00:14:41.351 --> 00:14:43.287
I'D LIKE TO PLAY
A LITTLE GUESSING GAME

00:14:43.287 --> 00:14:45.889
WITH THAT CARD
YOU'RE ABOUT TO THROW
OUT ON THE FIELD.

00:14:45.889 --> 00:14:48.225
A GAME?
WE'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF A DUEL HERE!

00:14:48.225 --> 00:14:49.993
WHAT? I'M ALLOWED
TO PLAY A GAME.

00:14:49.993 --> 00:14:51.962
MY TRAP CARD SAYS SO.
TRAP?

00:14:51.962 --> 00:14:55.766
I PLAYED A CARD FACE DOWN.
DON'T YOUR REMEMBER?

00:14:55.766 --> 00:14:58.802
IT'S CALLED PROPHECY,
AND IT GIVES ME THE RIGHT

00:14:58.802 --> 00:15:00.837
TO GUESS WHETHER THE CARD
YOU'RE ABOUT TO PLAY

00:15:00.837 --> 00:15:03.974
HAS AN ATTACK POWER
HIGHER OR LOWER THAN 2,000.

00:15:03.974 --> 00:15:06.276
AND IF I MANAGE TO GUESS
CORRECTLY, KAIBA BOY,

00:15:06.276 --> 00:15:09.546
THEN THE CARD IN QUESTION
BECOMES MINE.

00:15:09.546 --> 00:15:11.081
WHAT?
YOU CAN'T JUST--

00:15:11.081 --> 00:15:15.819
AND I THINK I'LL PROPHESIZE
THAT IT IS INDEED OVER 2,OOO.

00:15:15.819 --> 00:15:17.254
OHHH!

00:15:17.254 --> 00:15:20.424
BUT, WAIT. WAIT.
SOMETHING ELSE IS COMING.

00:15:20.424 --> 00:15:22.859
YES. YES. I SEE BLUE.

00:15:22.859 --> 00:15:24.061
I SEE WHITE!

00:15:24.061 --> 00:15:26.697
COULD IT BE?
YES! OF COURSE!

00:15:26.697 --> 00:15:30.567
I SEE THE BLUE EYES
WHITE DRAGON!

00:15:30.567 --> 00:15:32.002
UHHHHH!

00:15:33.303 --> 00:15:34.271
WAS I RIGHT?

00:15:34.271 --> 00:15:35.739
TELL ME I WAS RIGHT.

00:15:35.739 --> 00:15:39.042
I WAS RIGHT, RIGHT?
I SO HOPE I WAS RIGHT.

00:15:39.042 --> 00:15:40.911
ENOUGH! HERE! TAKE IT!

00:15:41.912 --> 00:15:44.481
[CHUCKLES PLAYFULLY]
HMM.

00:15:44.481 --> 00:15:47.517
NOW THE MOST VALUABLE CARD
IN YOUR DECK IS MINE.

00:15:47.517 --> 00:15:49.052
[THINKING]
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

00:15:49.052 --> 00:15:51.254
THERE'S NO WAY
HE COULD'VE SEEN
MY BLUE EYES

00:15:51.254 --> 00:15:52.522
BEFORE I PLAYED IT.

00:15:52.522 --> 00:15:54.791
HOW DID HE KNOW?

00:15:54.791 --> 00:15:57.394
PEGASUS MUST BE UP
TO HIS OLD TRICKS.

00:15:57.394 --> 00:15:58.395
YOU GOT
<i>THAT</i> RIGHT.

00:15:58.395 --> 00:15:59.896
[THINKING]
HE MUST BE USING

00:15:59.896 --> 00:16:01.932
HIS MILLENNIUM EYE
TO LOOK AT KAIBA'S
CARDS,

00:16:01.932 --> 00:16:03.800
JUST LIKE HE DID
WITH ME.

00:16:03.800 --> 00:16:06.303
POOR KAIBA. EVEN
HIS GREAT SKILLS

00:16:06.303 --> 00:16:08.739
DON'T STAND A CHANCE
AGAINST PEGASUS'
POWERS.

00:16:08.739 --> 00:16:11.008
NOW I HAVE 2 THINGS
YOU CARE ABOUT, KAIBA--

00:16:11.008 --> 00:16:13.977
YOUR DRAGON
<i>AND</i> YOUR BROTHER.
[CHUCKLES PLAYFULLY]

00:16:13.977 --> 00:16:16.913
HMM. LET'S SEE
WHAT ELSE I CAN TAKE.

00:16:16.913 --> 00:16:19.349
AFTER YOUR TURN,
OF COURSE.

00:16:20.584 --> 00:16:22.386
WITHOUT MY BLUE EYES
WHITE DRAGON,

00:16:22.386 --> 00:16:24.221
I HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT TO SWITCH
MY MONSTER

00:16:24.221 --> 00:16:25.222
TO DEFENSE MODE.

00:16:25.222 --> 00:16:27.658
GOODY. NOW
IT'S MY TURN AGAIN.

00:16:27.658 --> 00:16:31.128
[THINKING] HMM.
KAIBA LOOKS SO ANXIOUS.

00:16:31.128 --> 00:16:32.462
I WONDER WHY.

00:16:32.462 --> 00:16:34.631
PERHAPS I SHOULD LOOK
INTO THE MATTER.

00:16:34.631 --> 00:16:35.866
[WHIRRING SOUND]

00:16:35.866 --> 00:16:39.236
YES. LET'S LOOK
AT WHAT CARDS HE'S HOLDING.

00:16:44.207 --> 00:16:46.209
AH. A VIRUS CARD, EH?

00:16:46.209 --> 00:16:49.212
AND SAGGI
THE DARK CLOWN.
I SEE.

00:16:49.212 --> 00:16:50.814
YOU'RE PLANNING
TO CONTAMINATE MY DECK

00:16:50.814 --> 00:16:52.883
BY USING THOSE TWO
IN A COMBO ATTACK.

00:16:52.883 --> 00:16:55.485
BRILLIANT. AND NORMALLY
A MOVE LIKE THAT

00:16:55.485 --> 00:16:58.555
WOULD CLINCH
THE MATCH FOR YOU.
BUT NOT TODAY, KAIBA...

00:16:58.555 --> 00:17:01.224
BECAUSE AS SOON AS YOU TRY
AND MAKE THAT MOVE ON ME,

00:17:01.224 --> 00:17:04.327
I'LL HAVE A LITTLE
SOMETHING OF MY OWN
WAITING FOR YOU.

00:17:04.327 --> 00:17:05.562
HA HA HA HA!

00:17:05.562 --> 00:17:07.898
I'LL LAY ONE CARD
FACE DOWN ON THE FIELD

00:17:07.898 --> 00:17:10.701
AND ONE MONSTER
FACE DOWN IN DEFENSE MODE.

00:17:12.035 --> 00:17:13.637
AND I'M AFRAID
THAT'S THE BEST MOVE

00:17:13.637 --> 00:17:14.971
THAT I COULD
COME UP WITH.

00:17:14.971 --> 00:17:16.907
MY TURN!

00:17:16.907 --> 00:17:20.610
[THINKING] AND MY CHANCE
TO FINISH THIS DUEL
IN ONE MOVE!

00:17:20.610 --> 00:17:22.679
COMBO ATTACK!

00:17:22.679 --> 00:17:25.148
[THINKING]
INFECTING SAGGI
WITH THIS CRUSH CARD

00:17:25.148 --> 00:17:26.516
AND THEN
HAVING HIM ATTACK

00:17:26.516 --> 00:17:28.685
WILL SPREAD A VIRUS
THROUGH PEGASUS' DECK.

00:17:28.685 --> 00:17:31.521
EVERY MONSTER HE HAS
WITH OVER
1,500 ATTACK POINTS

00:17:31.521 --> 00:17:33.590
WILL BE DISEASE-RIDDEN
AND USELESS.

00:17:33.590 --> 00:17:35.625
WAIT. I REMEMBER
THIS MOVE.

00:17:35.625 --> 00:17:37.994
YEAH.
IT'S THE SAME THING
KAIBA USED ON YUGI

00:17:37.994 --> 00:17:39.262
IN <i>THEIR</i> DUEL.

00:17:39.262 --> 00:17:42.065
BUT THIS TIME, PEGASUS
IS GONNA CATCH THE BUG.

00:17:42.065 --> 00:17:43.734
Yugi: DON'T COUNT ON IT.
HUH?
HUH?

00:17:43.734 --> 00:17:46.136
PEGASUS KNOWS
THAT IT'S COMING!

00:17:46.136 --> 00:17:48.138
SINCE YOU JUST PLAYED
YOUR CRUSH CARD,

00:17:48.138 --> 00:17:51.074
I THINK NOW WOULD BE
AN OPPORTUNE TIME
TO ACTIVATE THIS.

00:17:51.074 --> 00:17:52.242
HUH?

00:17:52.242 --> 00:17:54.177
NEGATIVE ENERGY!

00:17:54.177 --> 00:17:56.379
IT DOUBLES YOUR CLOWN'S
ATTACK POINTS.

00:17:56.379 --> 00:17:58.782
AND SINCE THE CRUSH CARD
CAN ONLY BE HOSTED

00:17:58.782 --> 00:18:01.084
BY MONSTERS WITH LESS
THAN 1,000 POINTS,

00:18:01.084 --> 00:18:05.455
MY MAGIC MAKES
SAGGI THE DARK CLOWN
TOO STRONG FOR THE JOB.

00:18:05.455 --> 00:18:08.058
SO SORRY.
HAH HAH HAH HAH!

00:18:08.058 --> 00:18:10.460
[THINKING] HE HAD
THE PERFECT DEFENSE
ALL SET UP

00:18:10.460 --> 00:18:12.162
BEFORE I EVEN ATTACKED.

00:18:12.162 --> 00:18:13.497
BUT HOW?

00:18:13.497 --> 00:18:16.333
OH, WHAT'S WRONG, KAIBA?
YOU LOOK SO SAD.

00:18:16.333 --> 00:18:19.302
KEEP YOUR CHIN UP.
I'M SURE IT WAS
JUST A LUCKY MOVE

00:18:19.302 --> 00:18:20.804
ON MY PART.

00:18:20.804 --> 00:18:23.006
BUT YOU KNOW
WHAT THEY SAY, KAIBA...

00:18:23.006 --> 00:18:26.543
IT'S BETTER TO BE LUCKY
THAN GOOD. HA HA HA HA!

00:18:26.543 --> 00:18:27.944
AH! TALK ABOUT LUCK.

00:18:27.944 --> 00:18:29.346
MY DARK RABBIT.

00:18:29.346 --> 00:18:31.047
AND THANKS
TO MY DARK ENERGY
SPELL,

00:18:31.047 --> 00:18:32.382
HE'S TWICE AS STRONG.

00:18:32.382 --> 00:18:33.550
[GASPS]

00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:35.352
BUT I'M SURE
HE'S STILL NO MATCH

00:18:35.352 --> 00:18:37.487
FOR YOUR STALWART CLOWN.

00:18:37.487 --> 00:18:40.791
HAH HAH HAH--
UH--OH...HO HO...

00:18:40.791 --> 00:18:42.025
YAAAHH!

00:18:45.462 --> 00:18:46.897
OH, MY!
OH...
OHHH...
HUH?

00:18:46.897 --> 00:18:49.733
AND I ALWAYS THOUGHT
A RABBIT PUNCH
WAS A WIMPY MOVE.

00:18:49.733 --> 00:18:52.068
I'VE NEVER SEEN KAIBA
SO SHAKEN BEFORE.

00:18:53.236 --> 00:18:54.538
THIS IS BAD.

00:18:54.538 --> 00:18:55.806
Yugi: THE DUEL
JUST STARTED,

00:18:55.806 --> 00:18:58.275
AND KAIBA'S ALREADY
1,000 LIFE POINTS BEHIND!

00:18:58.275 --> 00:19:01.278
[GASPING NERVOUSLY]

00:19:01.278 --> 00:19:02.746
[CHUCKLING MALEVOLENTLY]

00:19:02.746 --> 00:19:05.315
[THINKING] NOW YOU SEE
HOW FEEBLE YOUR SKILLS
TRULY ARE,

00:19:05.315 --> 00:19:07.484
KAIBA BOY,
WORLD CHAMPION.

00:19:07.484 --> 00:19:09.486
HA HA HA HA HA HA HA!

00:19:09.486 --> 00:19:11.655
I MAKE YOU LOOK
LIKE A NOVICE.

00:19:11.655 --> 00:19:15.458
AND I'VE ONLY JUST
BEGUN TO MAKE USE
OF MY MILLENNIUM EYE.

00:19:15.458 --> 00:19:17.427
HA HA HA HA HA HA!

